2010-12-04 # 0.1-dev

The "site.firstposition" module adds SEO features to your web site : document title, document
description, google analytics tracker and google-site-verification.

The module alters the edit block of the "site.pages" module to add two fields allowing the user to
edit the document title and the document description of the page.

The module also alters the ouput of the WdPublisher to add the google analytics tracker at the end
of the document, before the `</body>` markup.

The `document:metas` and `document:title` TODO-DOC